0:21:47.220,0:21:51.299
But no more stories of the past, all told, all done.

0:21:54.440,0:21:56.710
Future stories.

0:21:58.190,0:22:01.609
I saw an onrushing storm.

0:22:02.180,0:22:06.759
The future comes hungry, for man and machine.

0:22:07.750,0:22:21.219
It will catch me I expect, catch us all.
