0:22:44.740,0:22:48.549
The Metal World, but not the one I sought.

0:22:49.130,0:22:53.480
The future is a frightful dream, huntress.
My name is Aloy.

0:22:55.440,0:22:57.210
I grew fond of you, your curiosities and disbeliefs, Aloy.

0:23:01.519,0:23:03.660
If you weather this storm, look for me.

