0:27:20.740,0:27:22.440
Handy.

0:29:43.450,0:29:44.690
Stocking up.

0:31:56.240,0:31:57.450
Let's see you catch us!

0:33:18.000,0:33:20.000
Always watching.

0:35:42.550,0:35:44.050
It'd be fascinating, if they weren't looking for me.

